Finally I got them to acknowledge that the error code on my washer was caused by an error, and needed to be fixed. But they insist that it's over a year past June 2025 already, and that my warranty isn't valid anymore. I showed them my receipt to prove it's still under warranty, and I guess they weren't expecting me to actually have it, cause now I got this in an email. Suffice to say, I'm a little irritated. But my only possible revenge is by showing the public how awful Samsung is. I don't want internet points, but I want this on the front page.
